title: Single cell RNA-seq analysis of oligodendroglioma
abstract: To understand the diversity of expression states within oligodendroglioma tumors, we obtained six freshly resected samples, profiled ~1000 cells from each tumor and examined their diversity.
overall_design:
Tumors were disaggregated, sorted into single cells, and profiled by Smart-seq2.

**GSM1812084 to GSM1815456: Submitter declares reads will be made available through dbGaP.**

**Sample records after GSM1815456: Submitter declares reads will be submitted to controlled access SRA and/or dbGaP. The sample records that follow GSM1815456 are incomplete.**
